<h1 class="text-center">How it works</h1>
<p class="text-center banner-subtitle">We collect, wash and deliver your laundry and dry cleaning in 24 hours.</p>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <!-- FIRST ELEMENT -->
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 process-card">
